<template>
  <el-menu
    class="el-menu-demo"
    mode="horizontal"
    collapse-transition="true"
    @select="handleSelect">
    <el-menu-item class="title">活动管理系统</el-menu-item>
    <el-submenu index="1">
      <template slot="title">个人中心</template>
      <el-menu-item index="1-1">基本信息</el-menu-item>
      <el-menu-item index="1-2">密码修改</el-menu-item>
      <el-menu-item index="1-3">退出</el-menu-item>
    </el-submenu>
  </el-menu>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: 'myHead',
  methods: {
    handleSelect () {}
  }
}
</script>

<style scoped>
  .title{
    width: 248px;
    font-size: 20px;
    text-align: center;
    height: 50px !important;
    line-height: 50px !important;
  }
  .title:hover{
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .el-submenu{
    position: absolute;
    right: 0;
  }
  .el-menu-demo{
    border: 1px solid #e3e3e3;
  }
</style>
